 <161369871+google-labs-jules[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 04:24:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 02/20] refactor(module): migrate connector model to
 Event/Control and map UI accurately

Splits the monolithic Trigger connector type into `Event` (discrete) and
`Control` (continuous). Maps trigger outputs and inspector mappings to
these new types while allowing backward compatibility in connections.
Updates UI to visually distinguish the new socket classes.

