Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 04:48:52 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 04/20] fix(nodes): Consolidate Effect, Mask, and Mesh nodes

This PR brings Effect, Mask, and Mesh nodes to the same schema and runtime basis.

1. Added `MaskType::File` and `MeshType::Quad` to the node catalog.
2. Updated Inspector previews so `Modulizer` and `Mask` nodes have visible preview panels like `Layer`.
3. Mapped `Brightness`, `Contrast`, `Saturation` effect parameters to `ColorAdjust` in the renderer.
4. Added UI warnings to the Inspector for remaining effect parameters that are not yet supported.
5. Gated `RenderOp.masks` in the render path safely by warning.
6. Updated the Audit Document to reflect the new state.
7. Fixed some minor build and test issues along the way.
